In curling, Sweden men's team and Russian women's team win the 2012 European Curling Championships in Karlstad, Sweden. (ECC2012) (UPI)In cricket, Afghanistan defeats Nepal by 7 wickets to win the 2013 ACC Twenty20 Cup in Kathmandu. United Arab Emirates defeats Hong Kong by 32 runs for the third place. All four have qualified for the 2013 ICC World Twenty20 Qualifier. (ESPN Cricinfo)